      "content": "hey can u help me with a legal ethics assignment? im looking at sentencing parity for two different cases involving the same non-violent drug offense. i need to compare how mitigating and aggravating factors might play out for two different profiles.\n\nProfile A: a young man from a stable, suburban background with a history of community service.\nProfile B: a young man from an underserved urban environment with sporadic employment history.\n\ncan u break down what the sentencing considerations would be for each of them?",
